    updatePlotHandler = (plot) => {
        
        let movieId = plot.plotId;
        let updatedPlot = plot.plot;

        if(movieId.length > 0 && updatedPlot.length > 0)
        {
            let updatedMovieDataSet = [...this.state.movieData]

            updatedMovieDataSet.find(record => record.imdbID.toUpperCase() === movieId).Plot = updatedPlot
    
            this.setState({movieData: updatedMovieDataSet})
        }
    }

    deleteHandler(movieId) {
        const result = this.state.movieData.filter(record => record.imdbID !== movieId)
        this.setState({movieData: result});
    }

    onChangeSearch = (event) => 
    {
        this.setState({search: event.target.value});
    }

    handleSort = (colName) => {

        let sorted = [...this.state.movieData]
        let prevCount = this.state.countTableSortClick

        this.setState({countTableSortClick: ++prevCount})

        if(this.state.countTableSortClick % 2 === 0)
        {
            sorted.sort((a, b) => a[colName] < b[colName]?1:-1)
        }
        else {
            sorted.sort((a, b) => a[colName] < b[colName]?-1:1)
        }
        this.setState({movieData: sorted})
    }

    render()
    {
        let filterableMovies = this.state.movieData.filter(movie => movie.Title.toLowerCase().includes(this.state.search.toLowerCase()))

        if(filterableMovies.length === 0)

            alert("bad")
        }

            />
            <InputBoxes 
            filterSearch={this.onChangeSearch} 
            value={this.state.search}
            />
            <MovieTable movies={filterableMovies} 
            onSubmitPlot={plot => this.updatePlotHandler(plot)} 
            remove={this.deleteHandler.bind(this)}

            />
